[9] New Zealand (Auckland) ex Philippines (Manila): alert
Date: Tue 11 Dec 2018
Source: News Hub [edited]
https://www.newshub.co.nz/home/new-zealand/2018/12/measles-alert-for-flight-into-auckland.html


A case of measles has been found in a passenger who travelled to New Zealand from Manila in November [2018]. The Auckland Regional Public Health Service (ARPHS) said the infected person flew in on flight PR218 on [Fri 30 Nov 2018].

It is asking for anyone who may have been in contact with this person to watch out for symptoms, including high fever, runny nose, cough and sore eyes.[...]

[Byline: Alice Webb-Liddall]

